domosaics.model.workspace
Class ViewElement

java.lang.Object
  domosaics.model.workspace.WorkspaceElement
      domosaics.model.workspace.ViewElement

public class ViewElement
extends WorkspaceElement

ViewElement describes workspace elements, representing views which were loaded.

The backend view is stored as ViewInfo and can be accessed via a ViewManager by getViewID().

Author:
Andreas Held
